Common support and utility classes.

Interface Summary
Duplicable<T> Refinement of Cloneable interface which enforces existence, exception specification, and return type of clone method.
 

Class Summary
Builder<T extends Duplicable<T>,B extends Builder<T,B>> A Builder allows (1) configuration of a T instance--the Builder's "prototype" instance--and (2) repeated construction of duplicates of the prototype instance.
ChannelUtils Adapted from Fast stream copy using Java NIO channels
FileUtils Collection of file utilities.
MemoryUtils Tracks memory usage by the JVM.
